room_title: Escape room "The Discovery" by Escape Reality Puzzle Rooms in Pittsburgh
room_description: A professor at Saint Vincent made a life-changing discovery. Potentially dangerous, this discovery could also be used to sustain mankind for centuries to come. Before Professor Lyle could reveal his discovery to the world, he mysteriously disappeared. He has left a trail for only the most brilliant to solve. Your mission is to find the plans for "Element X" before they fall into the wrong hands and get out unnoticed.
